items.name: Easy-.Plist-Editor-Swift
items.description: EasyPlistEditor is a class that create to insert custom .plist file to your iOS project where will copy to application resource directory when the first time application run and access the custom .plist file anywhere from your application to read or write. the custom .plist file will remain on your application resource until the application remove from device or reset the device. You can create NSArray, NSDictonary, Boolean, Data, Date, NSNumber, NSString variables within your custom .plist file and assign, use NSArray, NSDictonary, Boolean, Data, Date, NSNumber, NSString values anywhere your application.
